#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.151"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.151:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.151:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "12. Hard Work"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.151:0.3"
msgid "151. Nāgasutta"
msgstr "151. Dragons"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.151:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, himavantaṃ pabbatarājaṃ nissāya nāgā kāyaṃ "
"vaḍḍhenti, balaṃ gāhenti;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, dragons grow and wax strong supported by the Himalayas, the "
"king of mountains."

#. VAR: kusobbhe → kussubbhe (bj) | kusubbhe (s1-3, pts1, mr)
#. VAR: mahāsamuddaṃ → mahāsamuddaṃ sāgaraṃ (bj, pts1) | mahāsamuddasāgaraṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn45.151:1.2"
msgid ""
"te tattha kāyaṃ vaḍḍhetvā balaṃ gāhetvā kusobbhe otaranti, kusobbhe otaritvā "
"mahāsobbhe otaranti, mahāsobbhe otaritvā kunnadiyo otaranti, kunnadiyo "
"otaritvā mahānadiyo otaranti, mahānadiyo otaritvā mahāsamuddaṃ otaranti, te "
"tattha mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ āpajjanti kāyena;"
msgstr ""
"When they’re strong they dive into the pools. Then they dive into the lakes, "
"the streams, the rivers, and finally the ocean. There they acquire a great "
"and abundant body."

msgctxt "sn45.151:1.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto "
"mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant develops and cultivates the noble eightfold "
"path depending on and grounded on ethics, acquiring great and abundant good "
"qualities."

msgctxt "sn45.151:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto "
"mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesu?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant develop the noble eightfold path depending on and "
"grounded on ethics, acquiring great and abundant good qualities?"

msgctxt "sn45.151:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.151:1.6"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto "
"mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesū”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path "
"depending on and grounded on ethics, acquiring great and abundant good "
"qualities.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.151:1.7"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
